And Achilles answered, "Fear not, but speak as it is borne in upon you from
heaven, for by Apollo, Calchas, to whom you pray, and whose oracles you
reveal to us, not a Danaan at our ships shall lay his hand upon you, while
I yet live to look upon the face of the earth- no, not though you name
Agamemnon himself, who is by far the foremost of the Achaeans."
